data.description: Gorgeous home!  Have you been looking for the perfect home in Cherry Blossom? Look no further!  This home is only 6 years old and boasts fresh paint throughout, new roof, new flooring throughout the majority of the home and abundant space to spread out!  Upon entering the home, you'll get all of the cozy vibes of an inviting living space.  The open concept allows for the perfect space for holiday and family gatherings.  This home has so much to offer! Call today for a private showing!
